title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 51] Power Pop, Paisley Underground
description:
Here are four awesome, but sadly forgotten records of power pop and paisley underground style. Highly recommended for today's youth in search of great lost tunes and older guys filling in the blanks in their collection. Enjoy and keep seeding. 


Crash Street Kids - Little Girls [1982]

Maurice & the Cliches - C'est la Vie [1982]

Rain Parade - Beyond The Sunset [1985]

The Act - Too Late at 20 [1981 ]
